# Towards out-of-distribution generalizable predictions of chemical kinetic properties
Zihao Wang
CSE, HKUST
zwanggc@cse.ust.hk
&amp;Yongqiang Chen\*{}^{\*}start\_FLOATSUPERSCRIPT \* end\_FLOATSUPERSCRIPT
